videos.author: MTGGoldfish
videos.title: I Build-a-Bogle  $90 Budget Magic
videos.description:
We don't get cheap hexproof creature in Standard anymore, but we can build one with the help of Toadstool Admirer by stacking up as many instances of ward on it as possible, all for just $90!

Today's video is brought to you by Card Kingdom. You can pick up some Magic: the Gathering cards (and help support the show) at https://www.cardkingdom.com/mtggoldfish

► Read more about this deck (full article): https://www.mtggoldfish.com/articles/budget-magic-build-a-bogle-standard
